cii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">六、话剧剧情介绍</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 1.47" class=MsoNormal><FONT color=#000000><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">《我不是李白》剧情介绍（时长</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>105</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">分钟）</SPAN></B><STRONG><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: ''Trebuchet MS'',''sans-serif''; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-WEIGHT: normal" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></STRONG></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT color=#000000><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">为了给哥哥赢得摆平经济纠纷的时间，身为公司法人的弟弟李响甘愿到精神病院装疯，称自己是诗仙</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">李白</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">。当李响一边享受着装疯的快感，嘲笑着真疯子们各种令人捧腹的行为，一边等着哥哥来接他回去的时候，一封信改变了一切。哥哥携款逃走。</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">手足的背叛，使李响瞬间跌入谷底，自此他把自己变成真的疯子，变成真的<SPAN lang=EN-US>“</SPAN>李</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">白”。美丽的护士看到发生的一切，决定动员精神病院所有的疯子，这里住着三个正真的精神病人：一个是想出名疯了的</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">白兰度</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">、一个是骗人骗得忘了自己是谁的</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">某某</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">、还有一个是想当官想疯了的</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">领导</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">他们与</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">李白</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt">相遇了，于是，护士、真病人、假病人混成一团，笑料百出。<SPAN style="LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt">这是一出略带象征与怪诞色彩的都市喜剧，直面当代社会人际关系的交错、复杂，也展示了人性的温暖和善良。</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LETTER-SPACING: 0.4pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 2em" class=MsoNormal><FONT color=#000000><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">七、现场布置</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 2em" class=MsoNormal><FONT color=#000000><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">每次活动前</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">天搭建舞台，现场宣传喷绘在</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><S