-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">著名管理培训专家<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=center><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">方永飞<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE>\r\n<P class=0 style="VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">上课时间为：上午<SPAN lang=EN-US>8:30-11:30</SPAN>； 下午<SPAN lang=EN-US>13:00-16:00<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=0 style="VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">二、培训地点<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=0 style="VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; TEXT-INDENT: 27.45pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">宁波创新港（宁波研发园区<SPAN lang=EN-US>7</SPAN>号楼下沉式广场）<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=0 style="VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; TEXT-INDENT: 27.55pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">三、培训对象</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"> <B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN-TOP: 5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 20px"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt">宁波国家高新区区内重点企业经营管理人员等约100左右人。<SPAN lang=EN-US> <o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P class=0 style="VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; TEXT-INDENT: 27.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">四、培训报名<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=0 style="VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; TEXT-INDENT: 27.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312">请各企业根据培训课题，结合自身需求情况，于<SPAN lang=EN-US>11</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>23</SPAN>日前将参训人员报名表报高新区人劳局（人力中心）。届时根据报名情况领取培训门票，凭票入场参训。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=0 style="VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; TEXT-INDENT: 27.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312"></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312">高新区人劳局（人力中心）联系电话：<SPAN lang=EN-US>87909644<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=0 style="VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; TEXT-INDENT: 27.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312"><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312">传真：<SPAN lang=EN-US>87782411<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=0 style="VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; TEXT-INDENT: 27.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312"><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"></SPAN></SPAN>联系人：朱享梅</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312">高新区人劳局（组织部）<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=0 style="VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; TEXT-INDENT: 27.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" align=right><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312">二<SPAN lang=EN-US>0</SPAN>一<SPAN lang=EN-US>0</SPAN>年十一月十七日</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=0 style="VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; TEXT-INDENT: 27.75pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312"><IMG src="/hcms/sEdit/images/common.gif" align=absMiddle><A href="/uploadfile/attahces/201011181290050695.rar" target=_blank>2010年宁波国家高新区高级经理人报名表.rar</A></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>', '软件园管理服务中心');
