#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"></SPAN></st1:chsdate>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; TEXT-ALIGN: right; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto" align=left><st1:chsdate w:st="on" IsROCDate="False" IsLunarDate="False" Day="9" Month="12" Year="2010"><SPAN style="COLOR: #525052; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><IMG src="/hcms/sEdit/images/common.gif" align=absMiddle><A href="/uploadfile/attahces/201012131292226845.rar" target=_blank>培训议程.rar</A></SPAN></st1:chsdate><SPAN lang=EN-US style="COLOR: #525052; LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: &#718;&#805;; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>', '宁波产业园区'),
(1283, '<P align=left>各有关单位：</P>\r\n<P align=left>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 为全面推进高新技术企业利用国家高新技术企业所得税优惠政策和持续开展科技创新活动，进一步规范、高效地开展我区高新技术企业认定及复审工作，我区决定召开高新技术企业培训会议，特邀市科技局有关负责同志主讲。现将有关事项通知如下：</P>\r\n<P align=left>　　一、时间和地点</P>\r\n<P align=left>　　时间：2010年12月16日（星期四）9:00－11：00；</P>\r\n<P align=left>　　地点：研发园区5号楼208会议室(高新区杨帆路999弄)。</P>\r\n<P align=left>　　二、培训内容</P>\r\n<P align=left>　　1、高新技术企业认定与复审政策；</P>\r\n<P align=left>　　2、《高新技术企业认定管理办法》和《高新技术企业认定管理工作指引》解读；</P>\r\n<P align=left>　　3、认定、复审注意事项；</P>\r\n<P align=left>　　4、交流答疑。</P>\r\n<P align=left>　　三、参加人员</P>\r\n<P align=left>　　1、2008年已认定高新技术企业的单位负责人、财务人员各1人；</P>\r\n<P align=left>　　2、有意2011年申报高新技术企业的单位负责人、认定工作负责人各1人。</P>\r\n<P align=left>　　四、其他事宜</P>\r\n<P align=left>会议培训资料《高新技术企业认定管理办法》和《高新技术企业认定管理工作指引》，请在国家高新技术企业认定管理工作网（www.innocom.gov.cn ）“政策文件”栏目或宁波国家高新区管委会网站（http://www.nbhtz.gov.cn ）创新频道“公告通知”栏目（本通知附件）下载打印。请参加培训的单位于2010年12月15日下午16：00前将会议回执（见附件）传真至科技局。</P>\r\n<P align=left>　　联系人：徐忠华，王一锋&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 电话：87901979，87905697　　传真：87902097</P>\r\n<P align=left>　　E-mail：xuzh@nbhtz.gov.cn</P>\r\n<P align=right>　　宁波国家高新区科学技术局</P>\r\n<P align=right>　　二0一0年十二月十日</P>\r\n<P align=left><IMG src="/hcms/sEdit/images/common.gif" align=absMiddle><A href="/uploadfile/attahces/201012131292227779.rar" target=_blank>参会回执.rar</A></P>', '宁波产业园区'),
(1284, '<P><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px">园区各有关企业：</FONT></P>\r\n<P><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 16px"></FONT><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px">&nbsp;</FONT></P>\r\n<P align=left><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 周四12月16日将由宁波高新区科技局举办的高新技术企业培训，具体内容请点击如下网址：&nbsp; </FONT><A href="/cyzcdetail.php?id=1020"><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px">/cyzcdetail.php?id=1020</FONT></A></P>\r\n<P align=left><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px"><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 周五12月17日将由宁波市生产力促进中心举办的2010年度科技综合培训，具体内容请点击如下网址：&nbsp;</FONT><A href="/cyzcdetail.php?id=1019"><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px">/cyzcdetail.php?id=1019</FONT></A></FONT></P>\r\n<P align=left><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 16px"></FONT><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px">&nbsp;</FONT></P>\r\n<P align=left><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;请园区各企业安排好相关人员，有选择性地参加培训，并请尽快回复给相关单位的联系人。</FONT></P>\r\n<P align=left><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 16px"></FONT>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P align=right><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 16px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px">&nbsp;软件与服务外包产业园管理服务中心</FONT></FONT></P>\r\n<P align=right><FONT style="FONT-SIZE: 14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;12月13日</FONT></P>', '宁波产业园区'),
(1285, '<P><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">园区<SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">各</SPAN>企业：<SPAN></SPAN></SPAN> </P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 32pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">接市节能专项行动领导小组办公室通知，要求各企业在<SPAN>2010</SPAN>年<SPAN>12</SPAN>月<SPAN>31</SPAN>日前停止使用空调，完成“十一五”节能攻坚之年冲刺阶段控电任务。为认真贯彻落实通知精神，现将有关事项通知如下：</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 32pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><SPAN></SPAN></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; tab-stops: list 64.5pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><SPAN>一、</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">各企业在今年<SPAN>12</SPAN>月<SPAN>31</SPAN>日前禁止开启使用空调（医院、信息机房等对温度有特殊要求的除外）。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; tab-stops: list 64.5pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; tab-stops: list 64.5pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><SPAN>二、</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">各企业要切实加强用电管理，按规定做好空调控制、亮灯用电等控制。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; tab-stops: list 64.5pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><SPAN></SPAN></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; tab-stops: list 64.5pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><SPAN>三、</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">各企业将此通知精神及时传达到全体人员，进一步加强宣传教育，树立大局意识，确保“十一五”节能减排任务的完成。</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; tab-stops: list 64.5pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><SPAN></SPAN></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-INDENT: 32pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">特此通知。<SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></P>', '软件园管理服务中心');
INSERT INTO `y_news` (`id`, `content`, `source`) VALUES
(1286, '<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">各相关企业：<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">为使企业能更好的了解和享受宁波市知识产权政策，提高企业的专利技术开发与应用水平，增强专利法律诉讼知识和专利保护意识，宁波市科技创业中心决定举办企业专利知识培训，现将有关情况通知如下：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">一、时间：<SPAN lang=EN-US>2010</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>12</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>21</SPAN>日下午<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>：<SPAN lang=EN-US>30<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">二、地点：创业大厦<SPAN lang=EN-US>609</SPAN>会议室<SPAN lang=EN-US>(</SPAN>院士路<SPAN lang=EN-US>66</SPAN>号<SPAN lang=EN-US>)<o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">三、讲课老师：杭州九洲专利事务所有限公司<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:PersonName w:st="on" ProductID="陈继亮">陈继亮</st1:PersonName>老师<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">四、讲课内容：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、专利申请相关知识及流程介绍<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、宁波市专利资助政策介绍<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">五、培训对象：企业技术、行政或知识产权相关人员。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">六、联系方式：陈敏杰<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN>87904996 <o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 98pt; mso-char-indent-count: 7.0"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">传真：<SPAN lang=EN-US>87907875<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN>邮箱：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312"><A href="mailto:cmj@nbbi.net">cmj@nbbi.net</A></SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: center" align=center><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 22pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312">参会回执<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: &#718;&#805;">企业名称：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<DIV align=left>\r\n<TABLE class=MsoNormalTable style="MARGIN-LEFT: 52.65pt; WIDTH: 384.1pt; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; mso-padding-alt: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm" cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width=512 border=0>\r\n<TBODY>\r\n<TR style="HEIGHT: 16.55pt; mso-yfti-irow: 0; mso-yfti-firstrow: yes">\r\n<TD style="BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: windowtext 1pt solid; WIDTH: 123.1pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; HEIGHT: 16.55pt" vAlign=top width=164>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-INDENT: 15.75pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=center><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">姓<SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN>名<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P></TD>\r\n<TD style="BORDER-RIGHT: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 5.4pt; BORDER-TOP: windowtext 1pt solid; PADDING-LEFT: 5.4pt; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; WIDTH: 135pt; PADDING-TOP: 0cm; BORDER-BOTTOM: windowtext 1pt solid; HEIGHT: 16.55pt" vAlign=top width=180>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align=center><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2