(1292, '<P class=MsoNormal style="LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 新宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">高新区各用人单位：<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 新宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">为满足节后高新区各用人单位的用人需求，促进城乡统筹就业工作，本中心将在近期组织举办“高新区城乡统筹招聘会”。现将有关事项通知如下：<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-INDENT: 23.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.96"><B><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312">1</SPAN></B><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312">、招聘会时间及地点</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312">时间：<?xml:namespace prefix = st1 ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags" /><st1:chsdate w:st="on" IsROCDate="False" IsLunarDate="False" Day="5" Month="3" Year="2011"><SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN>日</st1:chsdate>（周六）</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">上午</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体_GB2312">8</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体_GB2312">00~11</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体_GB2312">00<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 21.3pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312">地点：宁波高新区梅墟中心小学</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-INDENT: 24.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312">2</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312">、参会费用<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN-LEFT: 23.95pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-left: 2.28gd"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312">经审核确认的招聘单位免费进场（额满为止）。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312">3</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312">、报名须知<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 22pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312">请于<st1:chsdate w:st="on" IsROCDate="False" IsLunarDate="False" Day="1" Month="3" Year="2011"><SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN>日</st1:chsdate>之前与我中心联系，并将设摊确认函传真至<SPAN lang=EN-US>87782411</SPAN>，招聘信息电子版本请发至</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体_GB2312">nbgxq@qq.com</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2