 Roman''">会议内容</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 14pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; TEXT-INDENT: -36pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 57pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 57.0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">（一）<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">宁波生产力促进中心王剑荣主任致辞</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; TEXT-INDENT: -36pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 57pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 57.0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">（二）<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">宁波生产力促进中心熊仁章副主任致辞</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; TEXT-INDENT: -36pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 57pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 57.0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">（三）<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">中信银行宁波分行小企业金融中心总经理魏星亮介绍中信银行的信贷政策</SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; TEXT-INDENT: -36pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 57pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 57.0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体" lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-list: Ignore">（四）<SPAN style="FONT: 7pt ''Times New Roman''">&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="LINE-HEIGHT: 200%; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 12pt">中信银行宁波高新支行行长赵宏介绍中信银行高新支行的基本情况，重点介绍“奖励补贴贷款”、“发明专利质押贷款”“订单融资”三个创新产品</SPAN>